---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const skills = [
  { category: 'Frontend', items: ['HTML/CSS', 'JavaScript', 'React', 'Svelte', 'Astro', 'TypeScript'] },
  { category: 'Backend', items: ['Node.js', 'Python', 'Express', 'PostgreSQL', 'MongoDB'] },
  { category: 'Tools', items: ['Git', 'GitHub', 'Docker', 'CI/CD', 'Linux'] }
];
---

<Layout title="About" description="About z1won">
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-header">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
      <p>자기소개와 경력, 기술 스택을 소개합니다</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Who I Am</h2>
        <p>
          안녕하세요! 저는 풀스택 웹 개발자이자 기술 블로거입니다. 
          최��� 웹 기술을 배우고, 좋은 코드를 작성하고, 그 경험을 공유하는 것을 좋아합니다.
        </p>
        <p>
          사용자 경험을 중시하며, 성능이 우수한 웹애플리케이션을 만드는 것을 목표로 하고 있습니다.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Skills</h2>
        <div class="skills-grid">
          {skills.map(skillGroup => (
            <div class="skill-category">
              <h3>{skillGroup.category}</h3>
              <ul>
                {skillGroup.items.map(item => (
                  <li>{item}</li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Experience</h2>
        <div class="experience-item">
          <h3>Web Developer</h3>
          <p class="company">Your Company</p>
          <p class="period">2024 - Present</p>
          <p class="description">
            웹 애플리케이션 개발 및 유지보수를 담당하고 있습니다.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #06b6d4, #3b82f6);
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .about-header p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #cbd5e1;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .about-section {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    color: #06b6d4;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-section p {
    color: #cbd5e1;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .skill-category h3 {
    color: #06b6d4;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .skill-category ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .skill-category li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    color: #cbd5e1;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .skill-category li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #06b6d4;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .experience-item {
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.1);
  }

  .experience-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .experience-item h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    color: #e2e8f0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .company {
    margin: 0;
    color: #06b6d4;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .period {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0 !important;
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .description {
    margin: 0 !important;
    color: #cbd5e1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-section {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .skills-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
